Whelp! You found this!

I guess you could probably go check out my IRC script [Oracle](Oracle) and its Minecraft plugin component [RapidIRC](RapidIRC), and chances are that's what you're here for.

If not for that, I'm (trying to) develop some games in Python, you can check them out at http://github.com/Toofifty/Tittle and http://github.com/Toofifty/Driving-game

Cheers babe.
